This project includes or is inspired by the following third-party components:

1. Original Prospector Hardware Platform by carrefinho
   - Inspiration: Community-driven ZMK dongle/display platform
   - Hardware Concept: Seeeduino XIAO BLE + Waveshare 1.69" LCD
   - License: MIT License
   - Usage: Hardware platform concept and initial display driver foundation

2. YADS (Yet Another Dongle Screen)
   - Copyright (c) 2024 Jan Fischer and contributors
   - License: MIT License
   - Source: https://github.com/janpfischer/zmk-dongle-screen
   - Usage: UI widget design patterns, NerdFont symbol mappings, LVGL implementation inspiration

3. ZMK Firmware
   - Copyright (c) 2020-2024 The ZMK Contributors
   - License: MIT License
   - Source: https://github.com/zmkfirmware/zmk
   - Usage: Core firmware platform, BLE APIs, configuration system

4. NerdFonts
   - Copyright (c) 2014-2024 Ryan L McIntyre and contributors
   - License: MIT License
   - Source: https://www.nerdfonts.com/
   - Usage: Modifier key symbols (󰘴󰘶󰘵󰘳)

5. Montserrat Font
   - Copyright (c) 2011-2019 Julieta Ulanovsky and contributors
   - License: SIL Open Font License 1.1
   - Usage: Display typography

6. Unscii Font
   - Copyright: Public Domain
   - Usage: Retro-style display typography

